title: Quickie: Rough N Rowdy Recap, Cops & Firefighters, Gay Pat's Walk Home and Dave's Ceremony
description:
Rough N Rowdy was last night. Gay Pat was victorious and did not get a ride home. Will cop vs. firefighter be in store for #RNR5 and does Dave care about anything?
